{
  "stem": "1338.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was in charge of that group.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And his responsibility was to bring 10 dead, so to prove, that, you know, that there was work done.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so there was very little survival in that-- in that particular camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called Dora Two or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a-- given a name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- well, I went to a couple of these things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first day I went in is they picked us up to pick up a train-- unload a train of clothing that came from Siberia-- not from Siberia, from the Russian front, which was actually very padded [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] clothing for Russian pilots or Russians-- you know, they had very heavily padded, beautiful uniforms.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first thing I did is got into the truck-- into the railroad car what I was supposed to help clean out into the whatever we do.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I dressed myself up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had beautiful, warm clothes, nice shoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was my first day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I continued sent-- be sent to one of those every morning to some of those groups to work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I saw that that survival was very slim.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wasn't beaten myself exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I knew that this is a question of statistics, you know, If you go like that for a month, you're not going to come back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, somehow or other-- I don't remember the details.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I wish I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a German Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think he was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was a German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That camp, by the way, was primarily run by Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the reason is that the Nazis never recognized the Geneva Convention vis-a-vis the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So they stuck all the Russians in concentration camps, as opposed to Americans and British, which went to stalags.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
